{
  "stem": "1062.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In there, nobody knew-- really, nobody knew what's going to be happening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What's going to happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People fenced into this area, and they kept on coming every hour and make announcement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anybody that has gold, jewelry, silverware, valuables, money, to surrender.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And those announcements were kept coming.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they made an announcement to anybody who doesn't surrender.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If he's going to be caught with the stuff, he's going to be shot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And people were very frightened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "A lot of people had some gold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, whatever they could get, money, something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took it along because we didn't know where we-- where we were going.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then one day, they took some women in one side, I'm talking-- I mean, Nazi woman, Nazi woman-- and Nazi men on the other side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they lined us all up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we went through and they searched us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Some of them were strip-searched, women were searched, you know, every place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as they searched us, they told us to go right across the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was a park.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We all went to the street.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And around that park, all the houses around that park, that was the main ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And from that park, we stayed there like, a night, overnight, in park.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The following day, they said, all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Everybody go into the houses there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because what they did during that period, they took away the Gentile people who lived there and they moved them out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the Jews were moved into this-- to this-- to this spot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we were-- and, and this area was closed in with a fence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they had the-- by the way, the Hungarian police who watched us, they were not the local police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were called border, border police.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
